message.content: cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.MM, cs.COMM, cs.SY - The paper discusses the feasibility of using mmWave massive MIMO for wireless backhaul in 5G UDN. This involves topics related to information theory (cs.IT), networking (cs.NI), multimedia (cs.MM), communication (cs.COMM), and systems (cs.SY). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
